name: Pablito
overview: Pablito is a game developed by Roberto Ricioppo using the Sideways SEUCK mod and released by TND in 2016. You are Pablito, a piece of toast, who is on a mission. You must guide Pablito around the maze and do battle against the enemies, in order to escape the maze to freedom. Can you do it, or will you become burnt toast for breakfast? Good luck.
